data.meta_description: Sep 14, 2017 - Anastasia Romanovna Zakharyina-Yurieva (1530-7 Aug 1560 age 30) Russia. Tsaritsa 1547-1560. 1st Wife in 1547 of Tsar Ivan IV The Terrible Vasilyevich Rurik (25 Aug 1530-28 Mar 1584) Russia. Child of Boyar Roman Yurievich Zakharyin-Yuriev (?-16 Feb 1543) & 2nd wife Uliana-Juliana Fyodorovna Zakharyina (?-8 Jun 1579) Russia. Roman gave his name to the Romanov Dynasty of Russian monarchs. Anastasia had 6 children. See more ideas about romanov dynasty, romanov, anastasia.
